="https://apps.shopify.com/lifetimely-lifetime-value-and-profit-analytics" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-schema-attribute=""><b>Lifetimely</b></a> <span class="acssf62a8">is a Shopify app created by Lifetimely.io to assist you in tracking, calculating, analyzing, and reporting profits and expenses to optimize your Shopify business.</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">This profit tracking tool is designed with a dashboard that monitors your gross profit and net profit in real time as well as compares your store to your rivals based on parameters like gross margin, blended CAC, etc.</span></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">This app also analyzes your marketing spend, including Facebook costs vs Google ads costs, to determine how much you have spent on product promotion and customer acquisition.</span></p> <figure id="attachment_3208" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3208 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app.jpg" alt="Best Free Methods To Track Your Shopify Profit &amp; Expenses" width="800" height="448" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app.jpg 1646w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-300x168.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-768x430.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-1536x860.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-400x224.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-800x448.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Lifetimely-app-1400x784.jpg 1400w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3208 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="Best F